Class SetTripleHandler

java.lang.Object
  edu.virginia.lib.fedora.SetTripleHandler
All Implemented Interfaces:
org.apache.any23.writer.TripleHandler
public class SetTripleHandler
extends Object
implements org.apache.any23.writer.TripleHandler

Utility class to produce a set of triples from a stream of triples produced by Any23 parsing. Most of TripleHandler's methods are unimplemented, because this class expects to produce nothing other than a Set of the triples emitted into it.

ajs6f
